Query.Statement: SELECT 1 as id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, (COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp),0) - COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp),0))*-1 AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Biaya Atas Usaha' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir] GROUP BY accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id

SELECT 1 as id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, (COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp),0) - COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp),0))*-1 AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Biaya Non Operasioanl' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir] GROUP BY accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id

SELECT 1 as id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, (COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp),0) - COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp),0))*-1 AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Biaya Operasional' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir] GROUP BY accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id

SELECT 1 as id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, (COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp),0) - COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp),0))*-1 AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Biaya Produksi' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir] GROUP BY accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id

SELECT DISTINCT 'laporan laba rugi' as name, a.ret_id, a.ret_group, COALESCE(a.ret_total, 0) as total_1, COALESCE(a.ret_persen, 0) as persen_1, COALESCE(b.ret_total, 0) as total_2, COALESCE(b.ret_persen, 0) as persen_2, COALESCE(c.ret_total, 0) as total_3, COALESCE(c.ret_persen, 0) as persen_3, COALESCE(d.ret_total, 0) as total_4, COALESCE(d.ret_persen, 0) as persen_4, COALESCE(e.ret_total, 0) as total_5, COALESCE(e.ret_persen, 0) as persen_5, COALESCE(f.ret_total, 0) as total_6, COALESCE(f.ret_persen, 0) as persen_6, COALESCE(g.ret_total, 0) as total_7, COALESCE(g.ret_persen, 0) as persen_7, COALESCE(h.ret_total, 0) as total_8, COALESCE(h.ret_persen, 0) as persen_8, COALESCE(i.ret_total, 0) as total_9, COALESCE(i.ret_persen, 0) as persen_9, COALESCE(j.ret_total, 0) as total_10, COALESCE(j.ret_persen, 0) as persen_10, COALESCE(k.ret_total, 0) as total_11, COALESCE(k.ret_persen, 0) as persen_11, COALESCE(l.ret_total, 0) as total_12, COALESCE(l.ret_persen, 0) as persen_12 FROM accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 1)a LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 2)b ON (a.ret_id = b.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 3)c ON (a.ret_id = c.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 4)d ON (a.ret_id = d.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 5)e ON (a.ret_id = e.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 6)f ON (a.ret_id = f.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 7)g ON (a.ret_id = g.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 8)h ON (a.ret_id = h.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 9)i ON (a.ret_id = i.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 10)j ON (a.ret_id = j.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 11)k ON (a.ret_id = k.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE, 12)l ON (a.ret_id = l.ret_id) ORDER BY a.ret_id

SELECT a.ret_id_group_summary, a.ret_id, a.ret_name, a.ret_sequences, 'TOTAL '||a.ret_name as total_name, a.ret_total as total_1, (a.ret_total / aa.ret_total) * 100 as persen_1, b.ret_total as total_2, (b.ret_total / bb.ret_total) * 100 as persen_2, c.ret_total as total_3, (c.ret_total / cc.ret_total) * 100 as persen_3, d.ret_total as total_4, (d.ret_total / dd.ret_total) * 100 as persen_4, e.ret_total as total_5, (e.ret_total / ee.ret_total) * 100 as persen_5, f.ret_total as total_6, (f.ret_total / ff.ret_total) * 100 as persen_6, g.ret_total as total_7, (g.ret_total / gg.ret_total) * 100 as persen_7, h.ret_total as total_8, (h.ret_total / hh.ret_total) * 100 as persen_8, i.ret_total as total_9, (i.ret_total / ii.ret_total) * 100 as persen_9, j.ret_total as total_10, (j.ret_total / jj.ret_total) * 100 as persen_10, k.ret_total as total_11, (k.ret_total / kk.ret_total) * 100 as persen_11, l.ret_total as total_12, (l.ret_total / ll.ret_total) * 100 as persen_12 FROM accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )a INNER JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )aa ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 2 )b ON (a.ret_id = b.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 2 )bb ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 3 )c ON (a.ret_id = c.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 3 )cc ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 4 )d ON (a.ret_id = d.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 4 )dd ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 5 )e ON (a.ret_id = e.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 5 )ee ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 6 )f ON (a.ret_id = f.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 6 )ff ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 7 )g ON (a.ret_id = g.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 7 )gg ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 8 )h ON (a.ret_id = h.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 8 )hh ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 9 )i ON (a.ret_id = i.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 9 )ii ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 10 )j ON (a.ret_id = j.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 10 )jj ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 11 )k ON (a.ret_id = k.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 11 )kk ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 12 )l ON (a.ret_id = l.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 12 )ll ON TRUE WHERE aa.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND bb.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND cc.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND dd.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND ee.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND ff.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND gg.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND hh.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND ii.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND jj.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND kk.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND ll.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' ORDER BY a.ret_sequences

SELECT DISTINCT 'laporan laba rugi' as name, a.ret_id, a.ret_group, COALESCE(b.ret_total, 0) as total_mb, COALESCE(b.ret_persen, 0) as persen_mb, a.ret_total as total, COALESCE(c.ret_total, 0) as total_ma, COALESCE(c.ret_persen, 0) as persen_ma FROM accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_awal]::DATE, [@tanggal_akhir]::date, 1)a LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_awal]::DATE, [@tanggal_akhir]::date, 2)b ON (a.ret_id = b.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_awal]::DATE, [@tanggal_akhir]::date, 3)c ON (a.ret_id = c.ret_id) ORDER BY a.ret_id

SELECT a.ret_id_group_summary, a.ret_id, a.ret_name, a.ret_sequences, 'TOTAL '||a.ret_name as total_name, c.ret_total as total_mb, (c.ret_total / d.ret_total) * 100 as persen_mb, a.ret_total, e.ret_total as total_ma, (e.ret_total / f.ret_total) * 100 as persen_ma FROM accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )a INNER JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )b ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 2 )c ON (a.ret_id = c.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 2 )d ON TRUE LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 3 )e ON (a.ret_id = e.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 3 )f ON TRUE WHERE b.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND d.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' AND f.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' ORDER BY a.ret_sequences

SELECT DISTINCT 'laporan laba rugi' as name, a.ret_id, a.ret_group, a.ret_total as total, a.ret_persen FROM accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_awal]::DATE, [@tanggal_akhir]::date, 1)a ORDER BY a.ret_id

SELECT a.ret_id_group_summary, a.ret_id, a.ret_name, a.ret_sequences, 'TOTAL '||a.ret_name as total_name, a.ret_total, (a.ret_total / b.ret_total) * 100 as persen FROM accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )a INNER JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )b ON TRUE WHERE b.ret_name = 'PENJUALAN' ORDER BY a.ret_sequences

SELECT a.ret_id, a.ret_id_group_first_level, a.ret_grup, a.ret_total_grup, a.ret_sequences, COALESCE(a.ret_total, 0::DOUBLE PRECISION) as ret_total, COALESCE(a.ret_persen, 0::DOUBLE PRECISION) as ret_persen FROM accounting.get_group_account_income_statement('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_awal],[@tanggal_akhir], 1) a ORDER BY a.ret_sequences;

SELECT a.ret_id_group_detail, a.ret_account_code, a.ret_account_name, a.ret_level_coa, a.ret_total, a.ret_persen FROM accounting.get_account_income_statement(1, [@tanggal_awal], [@tanggal_akhir]) a ORDER BY a.ret_account_code
SELECT * FROM company.get_report_company_profile()

SELECT iif( a.ret_account_code IS NOT NULL = TRUE, (a.ret_account_code || ' - ' || a.ret_account)::VARCHAR, a.ret_account ) AS ret_keterangan, a.ret_end_balance, a.ret_account_level FROM accounting.get_gross_income_formatx([@tanggal_awal], [@tanggal_akhir]) a
SELECT 'laporan laba rugi' as name, date_part('day', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) || ' ' || master.get_month_name([@tanggal_akhir])||' '||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as month_now

SELECT 'laporan laba rugi' as name, 'Jan-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as jan, COALESCE(SUM(a.ret_total), 0) as total_1, 'Feb-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as feb, COALESCE(SUM(b.ret_total), 0) as total_2, 'Mar-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as mar, COALESCE(SUM(c.ret_total), 0) as total_3, 'Apr-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as apr, COALESCE(SUM(d.ret_total), 0) as total_4, 'May-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as may, COALESCE(SUM(e.ret_total), 0) as total_5, 'Jun-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as jun, COALESCE(SUM(f.ret_total), 0) as total_6, 'Jul-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as jul, COALESCE(SUM(g.ret_total), 0) as total_7, 'Aug-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as aug, COALESCE(SUM(h.ret_total), 0) as total_8, 'Sep-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as sep, COALESCE(SUM(i.ret_total), 0) as total_9, 'Oct-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as oct, COALESCE(SUM(j.ret_total), 0) as total_10, 'Nov-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as nov, COALESCE(SUM(k.ret_total), 0) as total_11, 'Des-'||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as des, COALESCE(SUM(l.ret_total), 0) as total_12, 'JUMLAH BIAYA' as total_name FROM accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )a LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 2 )b ON (a.ret_id = b.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 3 )c ON (a.ret_id = c.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 4 )d ON (a.ret_id = d.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 5 )e ON (a.ret_id = e.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 6 )f ON (a.ret_id = f.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 7 )g ON (a.ret_id = g.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 8 )h ON (a.ret_id = h.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 9 )i ON (a.ret_id = i.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 10 )j ON (a.ret_id = j.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 11 )k ON (a.ret_id = k.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status_monthly('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 12 )l ON (a.ret_id = l.ret_id) INNER JOIN ( SELECT x.id FROM accounting.report_group_first_level_account x WHERE x.is_expense AND NOT x.is_deleted )y ON (a.ret_id = y.id AND b.ret_id = y.id AND c.ret_id = y.id AND d.ret_id = y.id AND e.ret_id = y.id AND f.ret_id = y.id AND g.ret_id = y.id AND h.ret_id = y.id AND i.ret_id = y.id AND j.ret_id = y.id AND k.ret_id = y.id AND l.ret_id = y.id)

SELECT 'laporan laba rugi' as name, 'Accumulation Jan'||' - '||LEFT(master.get_month_name(cast(date_trunc('month', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as date) - 1), 3)||' '||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as month_before, LEFT(master.get_month_name([@tanggal_akhir]), 3)||' '||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as month_now, 'Accumulation Jan'||' - '||LEFT(master.get_month_name([@tanggal_akhir]), 3)||' '||date_part('year', [@tanggal_akhir]::DATE) as month_accumulation, 'JUMLAH BIAYA' as total_name, COALESCE(SUM(b.ret_total), 0) as total_mb, COALESCE(SUM(a.ret_total), 0) as total_mn, COALESCE(SUM(c.ret_total), 0) as total_ma FROM accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 1 )a LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 2 )b ON (a.ret_id = b.ret_id) LEFT JOIN accounting.get_group_first_level_by_status('Laporan Laba Rugi', [@tanggal_akhir], 3 )c ON (a.ret_id = c.ret_id) INNER JOIN ( SELECT x.id FROM accounting.report_group_first_level_account x WHERE x.is_expense AND NOT x.is_deleted )y ON (a.ret_id = y.id AND b.ret_id = y.id AND c.ret_id = y.id)

SELECT iif( a.ret_account_code IS NOT NULL = TRUE, (a.ret_account_code || ' - ' || a.ret_account)::VARCHAR, a.ret_account ) AS ret_keterangan, a.ret_end_balance, a.ret_account_level FROM accounting.get_net_income_formatx([@tanggal_awal], [@tanggal_akhir]) a

SELECT iif( a.ret_account_code IS NOT NULL = TRUE, (a.ret_account_code || ' - ' || a.ret_account)::VARCHAR, a.ret_account ) AS ret_keterangan, a.ret_end_balance, a.ret_account_level FROM accounting.get_net_sales_accounts_formatx([@tanggal_awal], [@tanggal_akhir]) a

SELECT pd.id, pd.account_type_name, pd.account_code, pd.account_name, COALESCE(SUM(pd.saldo),0)*-1 as saldo FROM(SELECT 1 as id, accounting.account_types.account_type_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp - accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Pendapatan Usaha' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir])pd
GROUP BY pd.id, pd.account_type_name, pd.account_code, pd.account_name

SELECT 1 as id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, (COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp),0) - COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp),0))*-1 AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Pendapatan Diluar Usaha' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir] GROUP BY accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id

SELECT 1 as id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, (COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.debit_rp),0) - COALESCE(SUM(accounting.journal_detail.credit_rp),0))*-1 AS saldo FROM accounting.chart_of_accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.account_types ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id = accounting.account_types.id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal_detail ON (accounting.chart_of_accounts.id = accounting.journal_detail.account_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN accounting.journal ON (accounting.journal_detail.journal_id = accounting.journal.id) WHERE accounting.journal.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.journal_detail.is_deleted = FALSE AND accounting.chart_of_accounts.id IN (SELECT master.preparation.account_id FROM master.preparation WHERE master.preparation.status = 'Pengeluaran Lain-lain' AND master.preparation.fuction = 'Laporan Laba Rugi') AND accounting.journal.transaction_date BETWEEN [@tanggal_awal] AND [@tanggal_akhir] GROUP BY accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_code, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_name, accounting.chart_of_accounts.account_type_id
SELECT master.company_profile.id, master.company_profile.company_name FROM master.company_profile ORDER BY master.company_profile.id
SELECT * FROM (SELECT 1 as id, 'Income Statement' as name UNION SELECT 2 as id, 'Income Statement Summary' as name UNION SELECT 3 as id, 'Income Statement Comparison' as name)a ORDER BY a.id
select 1 as id
SELECT master.month.id, master.month.month_name FROM master.month
SELECT master.year.id, master.year.tahun FROM master.year ORDER BY master.year.id
SELECT 1 AS id, 'Internal' AS diperuntukan UNION SELECT 2 AS id, 'Eksternal' AS diperuntukan
